node.text:
Watch Chip spray our ‘49 Cadillac’s transmission tunnel with @3M Rubberized Undercoating and then a coat of epoxy primer utilizing the new #3MPerformanceSprayGun before installing it back into the #Cadillac.

#3MPerformanceSprayGun #3M
#paintbooth #chipfoose #foose #foosedesign #Cadillac #Caddy @3mauto @3mcollision

node.text:
Chip shares some words and a memory about his friend, renowned artist Mike Lavallee.

Mike is famous for his “True Fire” airbrush technique and appeared on numerous automotive reality shows including Overhaulin’, Rides and Monster Garage.

node.text: Build Overview and Rendering

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chip Foose in The Official Chip Foose. May be an image of text that says 'ROLL ROYCE'.

node.text:
I often get asked why I have a Rolls-Royce grille hanging up in my shop. 

One night when I was 12 years old, after working in the shop with my dad, he let me drive his 1956 F100 for the first time. Many of you know this to now be my truck that was done on Overhaulin’. Well back then it was lowered with big tires and no power steering. When I went to park after driving I was using my whole body weight to try to turn the truck. Unfortunately, I lifted my weight off of the brake and slipped onto the accelerator. Now, standing on the throttle, the back tires lit up and the truck lunged forward punching the front of the Rolls-Royce, then shoving it into a Porsche. My father leaned over turned off the truck and said, “Well son, you got all three.”

I keep this grille as a reminder. Things can happen.

Check out the video.
Every purchase supports Amy’s Depot, the charity I founded in my sister’s honor to raise awareness of Progeria, the fatal childhood disease that took her life.

node.text: Hey everybody, today I’m introducing a product I’m proud to be associated with: RUBITON™️ Pain Relief. It’s 100% drug-free, all natural, made in the USA and FDA registered to relieve back, muscle, joint and arthritis pain, almost instantly. I hope it gives you the same fast, long-lasting relief it gives me. Plus, every purchase supports Amy’s Depot, the charity I founded in my sister’s name to raise awareness and funds for Progeria, the fatal childhood disease that took her young life. With RUBITON™️ and your help, together we will help fund the cure, stop the pain, and help make the world a pain-free place for all! Thank you! @rubiton_pain_relief
